<script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function () {
        //FIX
        $('.content-wrapper .content-left-wrapper .box-islamic-section .box-islamic-section-content .box-content ul li:last-child').addClass('last-item');

        $('.main-nav-wrapper .main-nav ul li:last-child').addClass('last-item');
        $('.main-nav-wrapper .main-nav ul li ul li:nth-child(1)').addClass('show-img');
        $('.main-nav-wrapper .main-nav ul li ul li:nth-child(1)').addClass('first-item');
        $('.main-nav-wrapper .main-nav ul li ul li:nth-child(2)').addClass('show-img');
        $('.media-relation-wrapper div:last-child a').addClass('last-item');
        $('.correspondent-list li:last-child').addClass('last-item');
        $('.correspondent-list li:nth-child(even)').addClass('even-item');
        $('.page-listings table tr:last-child').addClass('last-item');
        $('.widget-sitemap li.singlepages a:last-child').addClass('last-item');
        $('.rss-page ul li:last-child').addClass('last-item');
        $('.ar .threedays ul li:last-child').addClass('last-item');
        // MOBILE > MEAMMENU
        $('.main-nav').meanmenu();
        // TOP NAVIGATION ANIMATION
        $('.dropdown').css('display', 'none');
        $('.main-nav-wrapper .main-nav ul li.has-dropdown').hover(function () {
            $(this).find('.dropdown01').stop().fadeIn("fast");
        }, function () {
            $(this).find('.dropdown01').stop().fadeOut();
        });
        $('.main-nav-wrapper .main-nav ul li ul li.has-dropdown').hover(function () {
            $(this).find('.dropdown02').stop().fadeIn("fast");
        }, function () {
            $(this).find('.dropdown02').stop().fadeOut();
        });
        $('.main-nav-wrapper .main-nav ul li ul li ul li.has-dropdown').hover(function () {
            $(this).find('.dropdown03').stop().fadeIn("fast");
        }, function () {
            $(this).find('.dropdown03').stop().fadeOut();
        });
        $('.main-nav-wrapper .main-nav ul li ul li ul li ul li.has-dropdown').hover(function () {
            $(this).find('.dropdown04').stop().fadeIn("fast");
        }, function () {
            $(this).find('.dropdown04').stop().fadeOut();
        });
        // TICKER 
        //$('#home-news-ticker').ticker();
        // CONTINUOUS MARQUEE
        marqueeInit({
            uniqueid: 'news-marquee',
            style: {
                'padding': '0',
                'width': '100%'
            },
            inc: 2, //speed - pixel increment for each iteration of this marquee's movement
            mouse: 'pause', //mouseover behavior ('pause' 'cursor driven' or false)
            moveatleast: 2,
            neutral: 150,
            persist: true,
            savedirection: true,
            direction: 'right'
        });
        // POPUP
        $('.NewsDetailPopupBtn').bind('click', function (e) {
            var $thisElID = $(this).attr('rel')

            e.preventDefault();
            $('#' + $thisElID).bPopup({
                fadeSpeed: 'slow',   //can be a string ('slow'/'fast') or int
                followSpeed: 1500,     //can be a string ('slow'/'fast') or int
                modalColor: '#000000',
                closeClass: 'b-close',
                follow: [false, false], //x, y
                positionStyle: 'absolute'
            });
        });
        // SLIDER
        $('#mostviewed-news-bxslider').bxSlider({
            minSlides: 2,
            maxSlides: 4,
            slideWidth: 141,
            slideMargin: 11
        });
        // NEWS IMAGE SLIDER
        var realSlider = $("#news-image-slider").bxSlider({
            speed:1000,
            pager:false,
            nextText:'',
            prevText:'',
            infiniteLoop:false,
            hideControlOnEnd:true,
            onSlideBefore:function($slideElement, oldIndex, newIndex){
                changeRealThumb(realThumbSlider,newIndex);
            }
        });
        var realThumbSlider = $("#news-slider-pager").bxSlider({
            minSlides: 4,
            maxSlides: 5,
            slideWidth: 156,
            slideMargin: 0,
            moveSlides: 1,
            pager:false,
            speed:1000,
            infiniteLoop:false,
            hideControlOnEnd:true,
            nextText:'<span></span>',
            prevText:'<span></span>',
            onSliderLoad: function () {
                $('#news-slider-pager > li').eq(0).addClass('active')
            },
            onSlideBefore:function($slideElement, oldIndex, newIndex){
                /*$("#news-slider-pager .active").removeClass("active");
                $slideElement.addClass("active"); */
            },
        });

        linkRealSliders(realSlider,realThumbSlider);
        if($("#news-slider-pager li").length<5){
            $("#news-slider-pager .bx-next").hide();
        }        
        
        // SOCIAL MEDIA HOVER
        $(".social-media li").hover(function () {
            $(this).siblings().stop().fadeTo("fast", 0.5);
        }, function () {
            $(this).siblings().stop().fadeTo("fast", 1.0);
        });
        homeThumbnailWidget();
        // LANG SELECTION
        $('.top-nav li.lang-selection').hover(function () {
            $(this).find('.dropdown').stop().fadeIn('slow');
        }, function () {
            $(this).find('.dropdown').stop().fadeOut();
        })
        //NEWS CATEGORY
        $(".content-news-category div.large-6").hover(function () {
            $(this).siblings().stop().fadeTo("fast", 0.5);
        }, function () {
            $(this).siblings().stop().fadeTo("fast", 1.0);
        });
    });
    
    // FUNCTIONS START HERE

    // NEWS SLIDER THUMB FUNCTIONS
    function linkRealSliders(bigS,thumbS){
            $("#news-slider-pager").on("click","a",function(event){
                event.preventDefault();
                var newIndex=$(this).parent().attr("slideIndex");
                bigS.goToSlide(newIndex);
            });
    }
    function changeRealThumb(slider,newIndex){
            var thumbS = $("#news-slider-pager");
            thumbS.find('.active').removeClass("active");
            thumbS.find('li[slideIndex="'+newIndex+'"]').addClass("active");
            if(slider.getSlideCount()-newIndex>=4)slider.goToSlide(newIndex);
            else slider.goToSlide(slider.getSlideCount()-4);
    }


    function homeThumbnailWidget() {
        //NEWS CATEGORY BX SLIDER 
        $('#news-category-bxslider').bxSlider({
            controls: true,
            pager: false,
            minSlides: 1,
            maxSlides: 8,
            slideWidth: 112,
            slideMargin: 0,
            infiniteLoop: false/*,
			onSliderLoad: function(){ $('.thumb-content-container .thumb-contents').css('display','none') }*/
        });
        //THUMBNAIL SLIDER HOVER
        $(".bx-wrapper .bx-viewport ul#news-category-bxslider li").hover(function () {
            $(this).siblings().stop().fadeTo("fast", 0.5);
        }, function () {
            $(this).siblings().stop().fadeTo("fast", 1.0);
        });
        //POPUP
        $('.NewsDetailPopupBtn').bind('click', function (e) {
            var $thisElID = $(this).attr('rel')
            e.preventDefault();
            $('#' + $thisElID).bPopup({
                fadeSpeed: 'slow',   //can be a string ('slow'/'fast') or int
                followSpeed: 1500,     //can be a string ('slow'/'fast') or int
                modalColor: '#000000',
                closeClass: 'b-close',
                follow: [false, false], //x, y
                positionStyle: 'absolute'
            });
        });
    };

    // WINDOW LOAD
    // ===========================================================================================
    $(window).load(function () {
    });
</script>

                    <div>تونس في 10 فبراير /<span itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization" class="publisher"><span itemprop="name">قنا</span></span>/ التقى وزير الخارجية التونسي خميس الجهيناوي، اليوم، بنظيره الدنماركي كريستيان ينسان الذي يزور تونس حاليا.</div>
